videos.description: Deandre Ayton blocks the perimeter shot and then hustles down the court to finish on the other end with a lay-in.
videos.headline: Ayton shows NBA talent on both ends of the floor

videos.description: Dusan Ristich gets hot from downtown as the Wildcats take a 26-11 lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Ristic drains back-to-back triples for Arizona

videos.description: Mickey Mitchell cuts backdoor and elevates for a massive one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Mitchell takes flight on one-handed slam

videos.description: Kodi Justice scores nine consecutive points for Arizona, cutting the deficit to single digits against Arizona.
videos.headline: Justice powers 9-0 Sun Devils' run

videos.description: Kodi Justice gets the ball in the corner and drains the 3-pointer to give Arizona State a 41-39 lead.
videos.headline: Sun Devils take first lead on Justice's triple

videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets his own rebound and finishes strong in the paint to get the basket and foul.
videos.headline: Ayton shows physicality on putback bucket

videos.description: Remy Martin gets the rebound off the missed Deandre Ayton 3-pointer and then beats Ayton down the court for the bucket.
videos.headline: Martin beats Ayton to rim

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright drives and throws a beautiful pass to Deandre Ayton who finishes with a strong slam.
videos.headline: Ayton extends Arizona's lead off pretty assist
